videos.description: Trae Young hauls a pass down court to Rashard Odomes who finishes with a slam for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young finds Odomes for slam

videos.description: Trae Young works around the defender on his way to the basket and finishes with the lay-in.
videos.headline: Young uses nice moves on layup

videos.description: Kendall Smith moves through a wide open lane and lays it up to extend Oklahoma State's lead.
videos.headline: Smith exposes OU defense with quick layup

videos.description: Mitchell Solomon finds Cameron McGriff who throws down an emphatic one-handed slam.
videos.headline: McGriff throws it down for the Cowboys

videos.description: Cameron McGriff reaches 16 points for the game by sinking a  long jumper to extend the Cowboys' lead.
videos.headline: McGriff stays hot with big 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young drains two back-to-back shots from deep to close the gap against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Young gives OU momentum with back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Trae Young makes a nice pass to Brady Manek who sinks a corner triple for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Young finds Manek for a 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young finds Khadeem Lattin and he finishes with a nice layup for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young drops dime to Lattin for layup

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff says getting stops and withstanding Oklahoma's run was key into their win in the first round of the Big 12 tournament.
videos.headline: McGriff says defense was key in win over OU
